sentence: Looking at options trading activity among components of the Russell 3000 index, there is noteworthy activity today in Salesforce.com Inc (Symbol: CRM), where a total volume of 135,893 contracts has been traded thus far today, a contract volume which is representative of approximately 13.6 million underlying shares (given that every 1 contract represents 100 underlying shares).
That number works out to 229.5% of CRM's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 5.9 million shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $165 strike call option expiring June 21, 2019, with 7,839 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 783,900 underlying shares of CRM.
